Detailed Description

Description:
: Start a property enumerator.

void TEE_StartPropertyEnumerator( TEE_PropSetHandle enumerator, TEE_PropSetHandle propSet );

For this test, we will need at least one TA.

Pre: Open a session to a GPTA.

Post: Close session and check that it succeeds.
